raw_text = "# SPDX-FileCopyrightText: The Threadbare Authors
# SPDX-License-Identifier: MPL-2.0
~ start
Bill has made it back to Valhalla.
He knits a large blanket for the gods.
Odin: Thank you very much young warrior for healing us.
Thor: You also defeated MAX TAXES.
Baldur: AND Cop Cough.
Bill: I was glad to serve you.
Freya: Our gift to you is the remainder of the threads.
Bill leaves Valhalla. He knows that someday, somehow, he will return.
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
